Company Profile:Pro Nutrition is a supplement store dedicated to bringing you the best and newest cutting edge sport supplements in the world to help you reach your fitness goals.We assist athletes, bodybuilders and fitness models reach their desired goals through supplementation, free diet plans and tips, and training routines. With Pro Nutrition there is no trial and error, we will give you supplements and diet tips that work, whether you want to build muscle or lose fat we can help. You have nothing to lose except the unwanted pounds of fat.We have a full line of supplements including but not limited to fat burners, proteins, vitamins, minerals, testosterone booster, amino acids, creatine, nitric oxide boosters, and protein cereals and bars. Our prices are also the best in the market making us the best supplement store for all your needs.
Job Description:• Full time position. Monday to Friday from 9:00 am till 6:00 pm. • Inventory management including weekly stock take, processing and packing orders, purchasing order, organization and labeling of goods • Accounting and will be trained with use of MYOB • Customer Service to handle enquiries, orders, phone calls, walk-in appointments.Will need to be willing to learn and preferably interested in fitness and nutrition products • May be involved in organizing events and roadshows as directed by Reporting Mgr • Marketing - handle and manages social networking sites, blog, newsletter, catalogue and sponsorship of events • Administration - handles paperwork with regards to lease rental, utility, stationery purchasing, freight and flights, liaison with suppliers and vendors • Source for events to speak and sponsor Pro Nutrition products, and handle the necessary admin issues and coordination
Please apply for this position by submitting your text CV using InternSG.
